data.description: **Assumable loan** for those who qualify!  A lovely traditional style home located in an established neighborhood backing up to The Dallas Athletic Club. Once inside, you will find a formal dining and living area that open to the oversized second living room showcasing a beautiful stone fireplace.  Outfitted with brand new windows, you will be amazed by the amount of natural light that shines through!  Overlooking the living area, you will enjoy a great kitchen loaded with amenities- granite counters, tons of cabinets, stainless appliances, and a custom dog door to the backyard!  A lg Master suite with his & her closets, ensuite bath with granite counters & updated tile plus an additional bedroom are downstairs.  Two spacious beds & one bath up. Covered patio & lg yard are perfect for entertaining. Lots of storage, privacy fence, 2 yr AC, 6 yr roof, & smart home features are just some upgrades!  Near parks, shops, & restaurants!
